title: Bug 116609[Regression] Color orange doesn't work.
description: Bug 116609 is a regression issue where the color orange does not work properly. When attempting to set the color to orange, it fails to take effect.
OB: When Previewing the report, the expected result of having the color orange displayed is not met. Instead, the color does not change to orange.
EB: The expected behavior is for the color orange to be successfully applied to the report item.
SR: To reproduce the issue:  1. Insert a report item. 2. Set the color or background color of the item to orange. 3. Preview the report and observe that the color does not change to orange as expected.
